{"tid":1113642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好灰","createTime":"2019-04-18T04:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T05:07:52.000Z","uid":162092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31797c3941c7ee18d867995e4fbedc3bb2ffbc08","tid":1113642,"uid":162092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近同女朋友分手<br />\n<br />\n佢：我想要係好鐘意好鐘意既感覺，但係我好肯定，你比唔到我<br />\n<br />\n佢：只要我鐘意佢佢偷食我都無所謂，點都好過同一個無感覺既人一齊，咁我寧願自己過，我想同我鐘意既人一齊，而唔係同對我好既人一齊<br />\n<br />\n一齊咗一年，一開始睇到佢咁講好嬲，但係諗諗吓佢又好似冇錯，最後變咗嬲自己比唔到感覺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f8a2fd72ce5ced32202b3e3eb45ec4d04d18e7","tid":1113642,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"算啦巴打<br />\n繼續嬲佢好過<br />\n嬲佢對自己傷害少過灰機"},{"pid":"80a4953d57fe90d5c412c15b1514f7c883e97459","tid":1113642,"uid":162092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"一直以來都話唔鍾意我<br />\n我只係當講笑<br />\n估唔到係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ad6bc07c03fdbecb833255dcb4ee401ee62077","tid":1113642,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a4953d57fe90d5c412c15b1514f7c883e97459","tid":1113642,"uid":162092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"一直以來都話唔鍾意我<br />\n我只係當講笑<br />\n估唔到係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n下個更好"},{"pid":"2520899639c9b656242ad85f1693dfde08c3f347","tid":1113642,"uid":162092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"睇到佢講只要鍾意 另一半偷食都冇無所謂 真係灰哂<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日本身都不斷做死狗，尋日睇完之後自己一個人落街行到三點幾先返屋企 on99咁唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問對佢唔錯 只要能力範圍都會做 以為佢係想要呢D 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我香港 佢澳門 平時一有假都會去搵佢 本身仲諗住可以同佢行到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該好難會有鍾意佢嘅感覺出現喺其他人身上啦"}]}